CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1956, pg. B13 reads: "Masters Of Ceremonies - The Rev. Leroy Patrick and Mrs. Ethel Ramos Harris took charge of the pageant and introduced the debutantes."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Rev. LeRoy Patrick and Ethel Ramos Harris, posed in Syria Mosque for Alpha Kappa Alpha's Fifth Debutant Cotillion
